data.description: **Seller is offering $5,000 in concessions/closing costs.**  **Refrigerator inside kitchen conveys; Washer & Dryer to sell FOR $1.00 AT CLOSING with an accepted offer! **Preferred Lender 1% interest rate buy down! (Ask me for more info to get another point lowered on your buyer's interest rate)**  **Solar Panels Convey (paid off)**  **Brand new water softener with filtration conveys**  Want a great home with a low-low energy bill? This home comes with fully paid-off solar panels that convey! You can't miss this beautiful home only 10 mins from LACKLAND AFB and within Northside Independent School District! Enjoy living in this awesome new community, Overlook at Medio Creek, right off 410 & Marbach, with a great community pool and playground. This beautiful 2 story home has a spacious, fenced backyard with a covered patio. The garage has built-in storage racks and large closets for all your storage needs. On the main floor, you'll find an open and spacious kitchen/dining/living room with a large office and half bath.  All bedrooms are upstairs along with a sunny loft area that can be used as an additional living room/game room/playroom.  Also, included is a brand new water softener with whole-house water purification. Close to 1604, HW-90, and 410 making your commute easy. This home is just down the street from your favorite grocery stores and food chains! Don't let this one pass you up, it has everything you need and more!!
